casebody.data:
Sire, Appellant, v. Merrick, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from first district court.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Van Hoesen, J.

J. Fromme, for appellant. J. Callahan, for respondent.

No opinion. Final order affirmed, with costs. For former report, see 6 N. Y. Supp. 661.
